HasRoles
========

Introduction goes here.


Example
=======

in a model class:
    has_roles [:first_role, :second_role]
and run:
   ./script/generate has_roles create_roles

now in the mode you can use:
add_role(:first_role)
remove_role(:second_role)
can_have_role?(:third_role)
is_first_role?
is_second_role?


